<h1 id="toc1"><span>Usage</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc2"><span>Note: This is a Black Highlighter based theme. You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. <a href="/theme:black-highlighter-theme">To learn more go here</a>.</span></h2>
<p>This is a BHL version of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604892858" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span>' <a href="/theme:pataphysics">'Pataphysics Department Theme</a>.</p>
<p>On any wiki:</p>
